{"tid":1220471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"616遊行過百萬會贏","createTime":"2019-06-14T04:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:49:46.000Z","uid":16925,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"011cfc24c98a332f70684975bc9059c4581bedba","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"夠人就好有可能延遲，所以 616  一定要出<br />\n<br />\n宏觀局勢<br />\n<br />\n1. 太多人同林鄭切割席，盲撐既政派都開始有動搖，以後管治如果硬推會變得困難。立法會議席下屆隨時有改變，其他佢想推既方案會變得困難。<br />\n<br />\n2. 國際太多聲音 包括台灣/ Theresa May/ 外交部/ Trump/ 德國佬，都有關注事件。好似係第一次咁多國家員首對香港事件表態。<br />\n<br />\n3. 上次遊行後太快出聲明引致既不滿，明顯莫視民意，引起不滿同後期既衝擊，影響民生<br />\n<br />\n4. 一開始用台灣殺人案作理由已經無左。 太多時間林鄭想送番比大陸既重點犯人，都應該走埋亦撤左資，所以set 完都未必捉到。<br />\n<br />\n5. 外資行同港商應該有憂慮，拖累香港地位及發展<br />\n<br />\n6. 警隊亦係政府既形象之一，今次太多把柄比人捉，令惡法真面目露出，做法更似大陸鎮壓手段，令人懷疑一國兩制變得漠糊。特別係今次延遲左開會時間，原本係內地封閉既消息係未通過條例前已經Leak 左出去比大陸人知。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">應該係想制做一個落台階，比多次機會政府係國際輿論同壓力再次反應。<span style=\"color: red;\">所以 616 一定要上街</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n係民陣既遊行先保持冷靜，之後一定要留守<br />\n但作好適當準備，可能仍然需要加比612 更多既壓力<br />\n唔好鬆懈保持gear on"},{"pid":"4e6c6537e77b749d93e62973a76a4413ad096780","tid":1220471,"uid":74368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b209c5549df53f30a7688e16ae6cfb6edbb2271f","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和平d ， 買定d 喉糖比耶蘇既門徒 ！！！！"},{"pid":"1763b6f89fd8739ec2dad46b0b46bf7af0dbe1ff","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"一步一步黎， 行左先 <br />\n<br />\n亦要虛張聲勢，大力宣傳進一步行動嚴動性<br />\n如果政府依然無動於衷，佢地今次會半夜/ 第二日即時開會，唔好唔計劃下一步行動"},{"pid":"458331df458a9e610f2a20799567bee9bdcfa12c","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一步一步黎， 行左先 <br />\n<br />\n亦要虛張聲勢，大力宣傳進一步行動嚴動性<br />\n如果政府依然無動於衷，佢地今次會半夜/ 第二日即時開會，唔好唔計劃下一步行動 ， 會準備唔切</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3cfb6635b0273e8b42c3945ffae48ff7eeeb1c91","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"Must go"},{"pid":"9ea31ca08c12bf49c10f15d8caaae12b5301649c","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"1c157926d8cb17fbef369324e57285e751ebcc08","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"出黎呀"},{"pid":"968cf701dea62c674bcb84916a0c8631801e5879","tid":1220471,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"一定會去"},{"pid":"eeb013fa710ae13016a63e8bf0d0c2d9b433eeb0","tid":1220471,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"夠大先有用"},{"pid":"d27fd2624a3206bb0401767e5d1c2e02d2f997eb","tid":1220471,"uid":171989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"70c7c5a75011b6e15adbb477af2673223850f3a5","tid":1220471,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7f93ee59a0eaaa891ef398f73a9fcacb1483431a","tid":1220471,"uid":228622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f52d3fc00037945c6d43146deec40d7d983d1d","tid":1220471,"uid":123115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"616 可唔可以帶啲物品<br />\n如花呀 旗呀<br />\n放低去政總<br />\n唔好畀佢屈細人數？"},{"pid":"7359f64a28e7a84dd3334a9917a5f5c97542c61e","tid"